# DAO Reentrancy Fixes - CEI / Guard / Pull-over-push
Network: Hardhat in-memory simulated network only. No live RPC or wallet used.

## Fix 1: Checks-Effects-Interactions
SimpleDAO_CEI: 0x5FbDB2315678afecb367f032d93F642f64180aa3
Victim deposits 10 ETH. DAO balance before attack attempt: 10.0 ETH
[expected revert] SimpleDAO_CEI blocks reentrant DAOAttacker.attack: execution reverted: "send failed"
DAO balance after attack attempt: 10.0 ETH
Attacker contract balance after attack attempt: 0.0 ETH
Recursive calls observed by attacker contract: 0
[assertion ok] SimpleDAO_CEI final DAO balance matches protected-flow expectation: 10.0 ETH
[assertion ok] SimpleDAO_CEI attacker received no pushed Ether: 0.0 ETH

